      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in immaculate, showroom-ready condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, untouched interior, reflects a standard of care that is rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. This is an uncompromising choice for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than excellence. We invite you to inspect a vehicle that remains virtually indistinguishable from its original delivery state.",
