    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely flawless inside and out! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it still has that wonderful fresh feel. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically perfect without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Swing by and take a look, I promise you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
