    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This specimen boasts a documented service history including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The atmospheric induction via individual throttle bodies provides an unparalleled throttle response, while the factory M-Variable differential ensures optimal power delivery. The chassis remains taut with original suspension geometry intact, offering the precise feedback and telepathic turn-in characteristic of a well-preserved M-car. A turn-key example for the collector who demands mechanical perfection and historical transparency.",
